    <h2>What is EcoTek?</h2>
    <p>EcoTek is an organization founded so that a team of students can collectively band together, sharing ideas and set of broad engineering skills to work on a major project that has a main focus on helping the environment, and ultimately compete in a variety of competitions to receive recognition and hopefully be able to insert our creations into our communities. Whether you have no experience with any type of engineering and only have an interest in the field, or whether you have already completed much relavent coursework, everyone is included. We communicate and teach each other different methods and think of ideas on how to improve our projects, with plans to have different projects each year...  
      EcoTek is a student run project organization that researches problems in our community and uses engineering and computer science principles to create projects that benefit the community. 

    </p>
